description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Bantu Spaceship performing live at the Conservatoire de Rennes 
Auditorium in Rennes, France, during Trans Musicales 2023. Recorded December 8, 2023. 

Songs:
Spaceships A Bantu
Sebenza
Bantu Electro Sungura
Bantu Cakes

Ulenni Okandlovu - Vocals
Joshua Madalitso Chiundiza - Synth and Electronic The Serpant - Guitar, Vocals 
Thando Mlanbo - Vocals, Rythm Guitar

Audio Engineer: Matt Ogaz
Audio Mixer & Mastering: K-Sann Dub
Arrangements: K-Sann Dub
Written & Composed:  Ulenni Okandlovu & Joshua Madalitso Chiundiza
Publishing & Label: Gros:Œuvre Records, Bi:Pole
Released Nyami Nyami Records, 2023

Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Alaia D’Alessandro, Scott Holpainen
Editor: Carlos Cruz
